=======================
 Authors of MDAnalysis
=======================

MDAnalysis was originally written by Naveen Michaud-Agrawal.

Oliver Beckstein and Elizabeth J. Denning are contributing to the
development and are maintaining the project.

Also see the project page
http://code.google.com/p/mdanalysis/people/list for a list of people
directly involved.


Chronological list of authors
-----------------------------

- Naveen Michaud-Agrawal (2005)
- Elizabeth J. Denning (2006)
- Oliver Beckstein (2007)
- Danny Parton (2010)


External code
-------------

External code (under a GPL-compatible licence) was obtained from
various sources. The authors (as far as we know them) are listed here.

libxdrfile
  - David van der Spoel <spoel@gromacs.org>
  - Erik Lindahl <lindahl@gromacs.org>

numpy.i
  - Bill Spotz

KDTree
  - Thomas Hamelryck (thamelry@binf.ku.dk)

DCD reader from catdcd
  - Justin Gullingsrud
